ported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "478752830280135"}, "review_messages": ["Thanks for updating those assets.  We will release the app tomorrow 8/22/2018 @10am PT", "Hi,\n\nScreenshot Image 5 is still not a screenshot.  Please update with a screenshot from your app.\n\nThanks.", "Congratulations! Your submission is ready to publish in the Oculus Store.\n\nYour app will be released on 8/15/2018 @ 10am PT for free under the Apps section of the Mobile store.  Let us know if you would like a different date otherwise we will go ahead and release it. Before the release, your assets do not meet requirements:  \n\n- Remove blue triangle from the Cover Landscape, Cover Square and Cover Portrait and move the logos to the center of the asset.\n- Remove in virtual reality, since the application will be viewed in VR this is redundant\n- The logo asset should be the name of your app not the studio who created it\n- Screenshot Image 1 is not a screenshot of the app\n- Screenshot 4 and Screenshot 5 are also not screenshot of the app.  They are screenshots of UI within the app.\n\nPlease do not update your online services (such as your back-end servers) or your build during your launch week.\n\nOnce your submission is published, you can access analytics [here](https://developer.oculus.com/apps/). ", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974449_220116535336708_7163835772750004224_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UP_IEXhwSIoQ7kNvgHl8ERv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDPht_vopv8iAnsRRmII5bVZ2Jl497DbKh2HFAJoEzTcQ&oe=674F059F"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Smoke Reading", "platform": "ANDROID", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1534893723, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "488095594949070", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "